{"tid":2433464,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"網傳中國推出入境旅客自行使用「肛拭子」採樣教學圖","createTime":"2021-03-05T02:25:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T02:34:34.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0404274909248c5f1a2f22f424082e1a0debdf68","tid":2433464,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T02:25:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/03/05/phpcJjC93.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F03%2F05%2FphpcJjC93.jpg&h=bafe5326&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國《泰晤士報》、美國《紐約郵報》以及其他外國網媒相繼報導，「中國對所有入境該國的外國旅客強制使用肛拭子檢測」，而中國國家衛生委員會聲稱，與標準的鼻拭子或咽喉拭子檢測相比，「肛拭子」檢測法具有更高的準確性，北京醫師也對此背書指稱，「如果我們增加肛門拭子測試，可以提高識別出感染者的比率」。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，中國為了「肛拭子」檢測法與其他國家爆發的爭端愈演愈烈，導致當地醫生建議官方媒體，旅客可以改為在機場「自肛」提供樣本，最新流出的教學流程圖顯示，旅客可自行脫去下半身衣褲，將棉花棒插入肛門約3到5公分，然後輕輕旋轉，接著將棉花棒放入採樣容器中，整個採樣過程只要10秒鐘。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3456787\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3456787&d=eRHmMhW6fCYgFX7Mu85bUgX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=4efea0eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3456787&h=2f217720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3456787</a>"},{"pid":"c663dd6b076c5119fbfc5f8fa779083e6e47e70b","tid":2433464,"uid":129664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T02:27:53.000Z","msg":"自己爆肛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過有冇真係撩到邊個知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9df27caf0c1336ac4b167437a21b3e4b2ee9fc9","tid":2433464,"uid":310311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T02:28:45.000Z","msg":"旅客可以改為在機場「自肛」提供樣本<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha